境问题** (environment issues) - the flows themselves are structured correctly fo
r when backend is available\n- But `setup.yaml` has a structural issue with `cle
arState: true` combined with expecting auto-login\n\nLet me fix the flows that h
ave actual structural issues:\n\n1. `open_drawer.yaml`: Change `assertVisible: "
