t if we remove `clearState: true`, the flow might be affected by previous test s
tate. The best approach is to add the login step.\n\nWait, but for `setup.yaml`,
even after login, without backend the app would stay on the login page. So the f
low would still fail in this environment. But structurally it would be more corr
ect.\n\nActually, looking more carefully at the `login` flow - it passed because
